  * SAUCE: Add sr_mod to the scsi-modules udeb for powerpc

  [ Stefan Bader ]

  * [Upstream] acerhdf: Limit modalias matching to supported boards
    (supersedes previous revert made by Andy Whitcroft)
    - LP: #435958

